*DB_File-1.811 (14 Mar 2005)

  14 Mar 2005; Michael Cummings <mcummings@gentoo.org> +DB_File-1.811.ebuild:
  Bug 84744. New version, first step in blocking perl-5.8.6 users from being 
  able to emerge older DB_File's since perl-5.8.6 comes with 1.810 
  - emerging anything less than that will override the core perl with 
  an older (deprecated) version.

  21 Jul 2004; Tom Gall <tgall@gentoo.org> DB_File-1.808.ebuild:
  stable on ppc64, bug #57585
  
  26 Jun 2004; Danny van Dyk <kugelfang@gentoo.org> DB_File-1.807.ebuild:
  Marked stable on amd64.

